short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows the user to interact with Google Calendar via 25Live data.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
WARNING: This extension is in beta phase!

This extension allows the user to select an available space from 25Live.  The space can update the location field in an open (but already saved) Google event.

Make sure to specify the root WebServices URL in the extension's options before using.
